# Writing tone

Writing style:
- Dry and official on the surface
- Quietly absurd
- Increasingly emotionally unstable underneath
- No internet meme slang
- No wacky exclamation-heavy humor

Examples:
- "Finance requires the receipt to become legible retroactively."
- "User reports urgency without evidence."
- "Thermal reserves object to leadership priorities."

Keep text concise:
- job title: 3 to 8 words
- description: 1 sentence
- result log: 1 short sentence